      libboost-iostreams-dev \

      cmake

COPY src /src
COPY include /include

WORKDIR /build

RUN cmake --build .
RUN strip tilemaker

COPY resources /resources
COPY process.lua .
COPY config.json .

ENTRYPOINT ["/tilemaker"]
